      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <strong>Synthetic GABA</strong>
        <p>Chemically synthesized gamma-aminobutyric acid. Less expensive to manufacture and found in most budget formulas. Some studies show reduced bioactivity compared to PharmaGABA, though it remains effective at higher doses for general relaxation support.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <strong>GABA + L-Theanine</strong>
        <p>The most evidence-backed combination for non-sedating calm. A 2019 study in Pharmaceutical Biology found this pairing decreased sleep latency and increased sleep duration more effectively than either compound alone. Synergistic alpha wave promotion.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <strong>GABA + Lemon Balm</strong>
        <p>Lemon balm (Melissa officinalis) inhibits GABA-transaminase, the enzyme that breaks down GABA in the brain. This combination extends the duration of GABA's calming effect rather than increasing its intensity. Ideal for sustained daytime calm.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

